  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  

Doug@defocus.demon.co.uk

In a message dated 95-10-20 21:53:59 EDT, you write:

>
>I hope '95 has sorted out this sort of thing, it would be nice to have a 
>viable alternative to Workbench for the future.
>
